      • ABContactResync

        public static GW_Events ABContactResync
        ABContact resync event. Generated only as a result of an administrator requesting an abcontact resync. All pending messages for the abcontact are dumped and the event is fired. Implementors will generally handle this event to dump the entire abcontact to bring the remote system up to date.
